🧠 5. The Engine (How it thinks)

Step 1 — Normalize

Convert all signals into comparable scales

Step 2 — Encode into voxel

Each location = state vector

Step 3 — Run Field Equations

We simulate:

Flow (movement)
	•	where people go

Pressure (competition)
	•	overcrowding vs opportunity

Gradient (value)
	•	where value increases fastest

