🎮 7. Matchmaking Layer (Game Theory Integration)

Borrow from games:

Aim for balanced but winnable environments

We define:

Success Probability = f(skill, competition, environment)

Goal:
	•	Not 100% win (too easy → stagnation)
	•	Not 0% win (too hard → failure)

👉 Sweet spot ≈ 50–70% success zone

